Navea, J. G.; Young, M. A.; Xu, S.; Grassian, V.H. and Stanier, C. O. “The Atmospheric Lifetimes and Concentrations of Cyclic Methylsiloxanes Octamethylcyclotetrasiloxane (D4) and Decamethylcyclopentasiloxane (D5) and the Influence of Heterogeneous Uptake” Atmospheric Environment 2011, 45, 3181–3191